linesOfText.text: Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't know you had a cold.
Sure would like you to open the door!
Don't cry, it's only a joke.
Police let us in. It's raining outside!
Lena little closer and I'll tell you!
I didn't know you were an owl!
I didn't know you could yodel!
Ben down and Jimmy a kiss.
I didn't know you were so happy to meet me!
Chicken the oven, I can smell burning!
